{"TopicId":162883,"ForumId":46,"TopicTitle":"Limit the Location Field","CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T16:28:56Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T16:28:56Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIs it possible to set a reasonable character limit to the Location field of our profiles?\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI realize it can be used for fun and to give a little personal flair to your account, but there are a few posters who shall remain nameless that are, in my opinion, abusing the seemingly infinite character capacity of the current location field.\u00A0 This results in a Location listing (for a particular user) that is 17 rows long, more often than not longer than the actual content of their posts.\u00A0 Another user\u0027s location field is 26(!) rows long.\u00A0 Its annoying.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nRather than setting the poster to ignore (I\u0027m certainly open to reading their quality posts), and not being able to turn off viewing of that portion of an account (the way you can turn off signatures) is it possible to limit the characters in that field?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-04T16:36:59Z\u0022 title=\u002207/04/2017 04:36  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 4, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by klesh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NSEP","CreatedById":165635,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T17:14:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWait the location field\u00A0has no limits? Quite odd in my opinion. I do agree with you yes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-04T20:30:01Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere aren\u0027t character limits to be adjusted, either for location or for posts in general, unfortunately.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-05T00:27:57Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOkay. \u00A0I guess I\u0027ll have to set them to ignore. \u00A0That\u0027s disappointing.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-05T01:16:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nJust to illustrate how obnoxious a one-line reply with a 26-line location field looks on the Kerbal Space Program Forums:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u00224wEeUFz.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022480\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/4wEeUFz.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, you\u0027re not lying, Red.\u00A0 I just checked another Invision Power Services, Inc board and indeed there is no limit there either:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022DFdnlMv.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022454\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/DFdnlMv.png\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-05T01:24:41Z\u0022 title=\u002207/05/2017 01:24  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 5, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by klesh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003Etested another Invision Power Services board.\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-05T04:11:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223111522\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499217388\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110814\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022klesh\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, klesh said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWell, you\u0027re not lying, Red.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTurns out I was mistaken, though. I\u0027ve turned on a length limit for the location field, give it a try now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"klesh","CreatedById":110814,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-05T14:24:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223111654\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499227883\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n10 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nTurns out I was mistaken, though. I\u0027ve turned on a length limit for the location field, give it a try now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOh wow, hey, thats service!\u00A0 I just gave it a go and the longest it can get now is 7 lines which looks good.\u00A0 Its long enough for a campy entry for flair, but isn\u0027t offputtingly long by any stretch of the imagination.\u00A0 Thanks!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI might have to pm you for the method if the fellas over at the DayZ forums don\u0027t know how to limit the field.\u00A0\u00A0 Thanks again.\u00A0 \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:kiss:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_kiss.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:kiss:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222017-07-05T14:24:56Z\u0022 title=\u002207/05/2017 02:24  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EJuly 5, 2017\u003C/time\u003E by klesh\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"John FX","CreatedById":59415,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T00:21:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI came here to start a thread about this so I will join this one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf there is a limit, it only affects new locations.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOld, long locations are still displayed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T20:08:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223112616\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499300471\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002259415\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022John FX\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n19 hours ago, John FX said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents ipsClearfix\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI came here to start a thread about this so I will join this one.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIf there is a limit, it only affects new locations.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOld, long locations are still displayed.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSoftware limitation, I\u0027m afraid. Changes to these sorts of things only get applied when the content is updated, same goes for the profanity filter and the acronym hints.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"John FX","CreatedById":59415,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T22:37:30Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223113393\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499371707\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n2 hours ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSoftware limitation, I\u0027m afraid. Changes to these sorts of things only get applied when the content is updated, same goes for the profanity filter and the acronym hints.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI thought as much but I thought I would mention it, at least the next person who comes along will (in theory) read this and have an answer.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThanks for stopping any more.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Kerbart","CreatedById":78303,"CreatedDateTime":"2017-07-06T23:06:31Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223113393\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022162883\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221499371707\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002